## Install dependencies
npm install

## Run tests to check if the answer is correct
npm test

## Task
Create a form like in the image products.png.
    - When the product and quantity are selected, the total price is displayed.
        - The products and prices are predefined in the App.js
    - There is a predefined component fot the result text so just the price need to be added there.
    - Add Dropdown component and set the placeholder to 'product'. Add also the needed state management.
    - Use InputSpinner component and set the placeholder to 'quantity'. Add also the needed state management.

